      "rationale": "Three systematically refined meshes (4.2 M, 9.8 M, and 21.3 M cells) were evaluated. GCI for the relative hemolysis index was 3.1% between medium and fine meshes, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The medium mesh (9.8 M cells) was selected for production runs."
