      "rationale": "Relative error in RHI was computed at each of the five operating points. Mean relative error was 13.2% with a 95% confidence interval of ±4.1%. Four of five points fell within the 15% tolerance band. The fifth point deviation of 18% was attributed to patient-specific viscosity variability inherent to the observational study design, not to model error."
