      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index is the primary regulatory QoI for CPB hemolysis assessment and is directly computable from both CFD stress-exposure integrals and plasma-free hemoglobin measurements. The mapping between computational and experimental QoI is well-established in the literature (Morrison et al., 2018)."
