      "rationale": "The observational registry used the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump geometry with the same impeller diameter and volute dimensions as the simulation model. Operating conditions (flow 2–6 L/min, speed 2000–3500 RPM) span the COU envelope. Blood analog fluid properties are consistent. Relevance is assessed as level 2."
